    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Immaculate older vehicle in truly mint condition and exceptionally well preserved. The exterior presents beautifully with a deep shine, clean body panels, and no notable cosmetic issues, while the interior is equally impressive with minimal wear, clean upholstery, and a like-new overall feel. It has clearly been cared for to a very high standard, and buyers can expect a vehicle that stands out well above typical used examples in appearance, condition, and presentation. A great fit for someone looking for a very clean, turn-key car that needs nothing beyond routine ownership.",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
