      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers dependable basic transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age cosmetically and is best suited for a buyer who values affordability and practicality over perfection. A smart opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone looking for inexpensive transportation with room to make it their own.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that won\u2019t break the bank? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a genuine, honest little runabout with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great as a first car, a backup vehicle, or a handy project if you enjoy tinkering. It\u2019s priced fairly for what it is, and I\u2019d much rather see it go to someone who\u2019ll get good use out of it than let it sit. If you want something cheap, usable, and full of potential, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Driver-grade project with solid enthusiast potential and a strong mechanical character. The powertrain pulls willingly, the chassis feels planted, and it presents as a usable platform for someone who appreciates analog feedback over showroom cosmetics. Expect visible wear, age-related imperfections, and some sorting to bring it fully up to spec, but it remains an honest, straightforward car with plenty of life left for a hands-on owner. A great budget entry for someone looking for a capable machine with real personality.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
