      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get on the road. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with honest miles and undeniable character, this ride is the kind of machine that still turns heads for all the right reasons: presence, personality, and possibility. It\u2019s not pretending to be showroom fresh\u2014instead, it offers a rare chance to own something affordable with real spirit, perfect for a hands-on driver, a weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for dependable transportation with a story to tell. If you appreciate vehicles with soul and see opportunity where others see ordinary, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable transportation with solid value for the right buyer. This vehicle is being offered as a budget-friendly option with clear cosmetic and mechanical needs reflected in the price. A practical choice for someone looking for an inexpensive project, parts vehicle, or basic local driver. Straightforward offering, priced to sell, and a great opportunity for a handy owner.",
      "price": 4950.0,
