      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s priced for someone who wants affordable wheels without spending a fortune. It\u2019s not a showroom piece, but it\u2019s a solid option for a handy buyer, a first project, or just a cheap runabout to get you from A to B. If you\u2019re after something straightforward, budget-friendly, and full of potential, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
